{"text": "Hypersensitivity to carbamazepine presenting with a leukemoid reaction, eosinophilia, erythroderma, and renal failure. We report a patient in whom hypersensitivity to carbamazepine presented with generalized erythroderma, a severe leukemoid reaction, eosinophilia, hyponatremia, and renal failure. This is the first report of such an unusual reaction to carbamazepine.", "sourcedb": "PubMed", "sourceid": "2522601", "denotations": [{"id": "T1", "span": {"begin": 0, "end": 16}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T2", "span": {"begin": 20, "end": 33}, "obj": "Chemical"}, {"id": "T3", "span": {"begin": 52, "end": 70}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T4", "span": {"begin": 72, "end": 84}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T5", "span": {"begin": 86, "end": 98}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T6", "span": {"begin": 104, "end": 117}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T7", "span": {"begin": 147, "end": 163}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T8", "span": {"begin": 167, "end": 180}, "obj": "Chemical"}, {"id": "T9", "span": {"begin": 208, "end": 220}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T10", "span": {"begin": 231, "end": 249}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T11", "span": {"begin": 251, "end": 263}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T12", "span": {"begin": 265, "end": 277}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T13", "span": {"begin": 283, "end": 296}, "obj": "Disease"}, {"id": "T14", "span": {"begin": 354, "end": 367}, "obj": "Chemical"}], "relations": []}